    "text": "BP 180.0/120 — প্রি-এক্লাম্পসিয়া! বাম কাতে শোয়ান, ১০৮ কল করুন।",
    "tone": "emergency",
    "key": "44c9832c5fafa38f054cbfa06d31d46c",
    "filename": "44c9832c5fafa38f054cbfa06d31d46c.mp3",
    "bytes": 32832
  },
  {
    "text": "Home care. Routine follow-up per module schedule. Counsel on warning signs. Record visit on ANMOL.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "98466b71bfbaab6503f96a250c9076a9",
    "filename": "98466b71bfbaab6503f96a250c9076a9.mp3",
    "bytes": 39552
  },
  {
    "text": "Refer to PHC within 24 h. Follow up in 2 days. Counsel on escalation signs. Record on ANMOL.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "f586704d76b1bb91f9711919b2829eaf",
    "filename": "f586704d76b1bb91f9711919b2829eaf.mp3",
    "bytes": 36288
  },
  {
    "text": "Refer FRU/SNCU/DH immediately (≤ 30–60 min). Call 108. Bengali action card displayed. Decision trace locked and stored. MDSR hook triggered if applicable.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "bc03b8ac35aaf08a11a37efd59c6a50f",
    "filename": "bc03b8ac35aaf08a11a37efd59c6a50f.mp3",
    "bytes": 60480
  },
  {
    "text": "শিশু বুকের দুধ খেতে পারছে না?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "6bb8d3707379025702563c110883aa77",
    "filename": "6bb8d3707379025702563c110883aa77.mp3",
    "bytes": 12096
  },
  {
    "text": "PSBI hard-stop. Refer to SNCU/FRU immediately (≤ 30 min). Do not delay for any reason.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "5ef9817122add353cccf56978c75c064",
    "filename": "5ef9817122add353cccf56978c75c064.mp3",
    "bytes": 37344
  },
  {
    "text": "শিশুর শরীরে জ্বর আছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "66b09c86f2311a3117b0b09176813a7e",
    "filename": "66b09c86f2311a3117b0b09176813a7e.mp3",
    "bytes": 10848
  },
  {
    "text": "PSBI hard-stop. Refer to SNCU/FRU immediately. Any fever in a newborn is a danger sign.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "317c2ff59a20f318258adce7a6d326fc",
    "filename": "317c2ff59a20f318258adce7a6d326fc.mp3",
    "bytes": 32640
  },
  {
    "text": "শ্বাস-প্রশ্বাস দ্রুত বা কষ্টকর?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "777fb3031991aff970d9ed69e03c0ed8",
    "filename": "777fb3031991aff970d9ed69e03c0ed8.mp3",
    "bytes": 14304
  },
  {
    "text": "PSBI hard-stop. Refer to SNCU/FRU immediately. Count RR — if ≥ 60/min = severe.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "a7ffa03d1fa41b8dd08bb2c2e15d96b4",
    "filename": "a7ffa03d1fa41b8dd08bb2c2e15d96b4.mp3",
    "bytes": 43008
  },
  {
    "text": "নাভি লাল, ফোলা বা পুঁজ আছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "9c549dd531eaa80c2f8b68ec8cf98657",
    "filename": "9c549dd531eaa80c2f8b68ec8cf98657.mp3",
    "bytes": 17280
  },
  {
    "text": "Refer to FRU/DH immediately. Omphalitis can progress to sepsis within hours.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "9dd2d9e438179c3584b0df1709cdaf00",
    "filename": "9dd2d9e438179c3584b0df1709cdaf00.mp3",
    "bytes": 24384
  },
  {
    "text": "শিশু অনেক কম নড়ছে বা নিস্তেজ?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "54b806531514ae7b2386f39178f83635",
    "filename": "54b806531514ae7b2386f39178f83635.mp3",
    "bytes": 12576
  },
  {
    "text": "PSBI hard-stop. Refer to SNCU/FRU immediately. Lethargy = severe systemic illness.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "555f0272c484596bb466593a34486466",
    "filename": "555f0272c484596bb466593a34486466.mp3",
    "bytes": 30048
  },
  {
    "text": "ত্বক হলুদ বা নীলাভ দেখাচ্ছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "e16a68f82c530aa7baa58ac3127eded9",
    "filename": "e16a68f82c530aa7baa58ac3127eded9.mp3",
    "bytes": 12768
  },
  {
    "text": "Cyanosis or jaundice within 24 h = refer SNCU immediately. Jaundice day 2–14 without palm/sole involvement = refer PHC within 24 h for bilirubin check.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "1bb711fa1a9868867d35fcbc041cc9da",
    "filename": "1bb711fa1a9868867d35fcbc041cc9da.mp3",
    "bytes": 59616
  },
  {
    "text": "সব প্রশ্নের উত্তর না — কোনো বিপদচিহ্ন নেই?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "533892cfabc247fd8f36f132a82c991f",
    "filename": "533892cfabc247fd8f36f132a82c991f.mp3",
    "bytes": 16608
  },
  {
    "text": "HBNC home visit schedule: day 1, 3, 7, 14, 28. Counsel on exclusive breastfeeding, warmth, cord care, danger sign recognition.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "6042aa47225f369f40db4a59727e5ec7",
    "filename": "6042aa47225f369f40db4a59727e5ec7.mp3",
    "bytes": 75360
  },
  {
    "text": "পাঁচ দিনের বেশি জ্বর চলছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "333f5a333a85230acf494bff8b4ef4e6",
    "filename": "333f5a333a85230acf494bff8b4ef4e6.mp3",
    "bytes": 11904
  },
  {
    "text": "Refer to PHC/DH same day. Rule out malaria, typhoid, dengue. Do not give antipyretics and send home.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "1255f3feb24950a858652393360b4e35",
    "filename": "1255f3feb24950a858652393360b4e35.mp3",
    "bytes": 48384
  },
  {
    "text": "কাশি বা শ্বাসকষ্ট আছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "e8437e737f977f291379ee0cd10e2a85",
    "filename": "e8437e737f977f291379ee0cd10e2a85.mp3",
    "bytes": 11712
  },
  {
    "text": "Count respiratory rate. RR ≥ 50 (2–12 m) or ≥ 40 (1–5 y) = pneumonia → PHC within 24 h. Chest indrawing or stridor = severe pneumonia → RED, refer FRU immediately.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "b3aba478c8b18cf5b443445025d621d9",
    "filename": "b3aba478c8b18cf5b443445025d621d9.mp3",
    "bytes": 116256
  },
  {
    "text": "ডায়রিয়া বা বারবার বমি হচ্ছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "7f562b5408e2e5269603685dd98b4ad6",
    "filename": "7f562b5408e2e5269603685dd98b4ad6.mp3",
    "bytes": 12576
  },
  {
    "text": "Assess dehydration. No dehydration = GREEN (ORS at home). Some dehydration = YELLOW (ORS at PHC). Severe dehydration (sunken eyes, skin pinch slow, unable to drink) = RED, IV fluids at FRU.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "8551fb73dcd9af7d9f93450058059bfd",
    "filename": "8551fb73dcd9af7d9f93450058059bfd.mp3",
    "bytes": 103872
  },
  {
    "text": "শিশু খেতে একদম অস্বীকার করছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "616c39abfdb4ed1beae650d6a0b56ea0",
    "filename": "616c39abfdb4ed1beae650d6a0b56ea0.mp3",
    "bytes": 13632
  },
  {
    "text": "Assess for illness cause. If associated with fever/diarrhoea = escalate to relevant rule. Isolated feeding refusal > 2 days = PHC referral within 24 h.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "d0a103f79d426348df8ca009465f421f",
    "filename": "d0a103f79d426348df8ca009465f421f.mp3",
    "bytes": 60480
  },
  {
    "text": "পানিশূন্যতার লক্ষণ (চোখ গর্তে, ঠোঁট শুকনো)?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "f14da3323c5fbf2b2a4353e607d47949",
    "filename": "f14da3323c5fbf2b2a4353e607d47949.mp3",
    "bytes": 26400
  },
  {
    "text": "Severe dehydration = RED. Start ORS immediately. Refer to FRU for IV fluids. Do not delay referral.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "1a36d5ff005b9b4e1d6240b82f9ca148",
    "filename": "1a36d5ff005b9b4e1d6240b82f9ca148.mp3",
    "bytes": 39936
  },
  {
    "text": "ওজন বয়সের তুলনায় অনেক কম?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "d4ac24e4e1993e89f4eac1efaa540ff1",
    "filename": "d4ac24e4e1993e89f4eac1efaa540ff1.mp3",
    "bytes": 12960
  },
  {
    "text": "Measure MUAC. MUAC < 11.5 cm or oedema = SAM → RED, refer NRC. MUAC 11.5–12.5 cm = MAM → YELLOW, refer ICDS/NRC for RUTF. MUAC > 12.5 cm = GREEN, counsel on feeding.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "93891db6adff7bfc3996c8e7e63472ff",
    "filename": "93891db6adff7bfc3996c8e7e63472ff.mp3",
    "bytes": 199584
  },
  {
    "text": "শিশু খাওয়া-দাওয়া একদম বন্ধ করে দিয়েছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "c03125282ca7d2cb2a4ffbd744394fac",
    "filename": "c03125282ca7d2cb2a4ffbd744394fac.mp3",
    "bytes": 15744
  },
  {
    "text": "Any feeding refusal in infant < 2 months = RED hard-stop. Refer FRU immediately.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "7fcca3ef57dc9b9e8fe33162c049eaab",
    "filename": "7fcca3ef57dc9b9e8fe33162c049eaab.mp3",
    "bytes": 35232
  },
  {
    "text": "তিন দিনের বেশি জ্বর চলছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "ac7818169a22de8408849a723a29f261",
    "filename": "ac7818169a22de8408849a723a29f261.mp3",
    "bytes": 11712
  },
  {
    "text": "Refer to PHC/FRU same day. Infants < 3 months with any fever = RED hard-stop.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "edc00f91f962e6aadb4d3129c0d5a508",
    "filename": "edc00f91f962e6aadb4d3129c0d5a508.mp3",
    "bytes": 32832
  },
  {
    "text": "Assess dehydration. Some dehydration = YELLOW, PHC within 24 h. Severe dehydration = RED, FRU for IV fluids.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "a16c8e3da1f60725c2c899469af80724",
    "filename": "a16c8e3da1f60725c2c899469af80724.mp3",
    "bytes": 75840
  },
  {
    "text": "শ্বাসকষ্ট বা বুকে শব্দ হচ্ছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "c272135396cfdb4bcbd50d9439cb9814",
    "filename": "c272135396cfdb4bcbd50d9439cb9814.mp3",
    "bytes": 12768
  },
  {
    "text": "Chest indrawing or stridor in infant = RED, refer FRU immediately. Fast breathing alone (RR ≥ 50) = YELLOW, refer PHC within 24 h.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "1f877ae633c2485197aab68bcba1a317",
    "filename": "1f877ae633c2485197aab68bcba1a317.mp3",
    "bytes": 87264
  },
  {
    "text": "Severe dehydration in infant = RED. Start ORS immediately. Refer FRU for IV fluids.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "7bb8ed3733ecde118369601db789d9f7",
    "filename": "7bb8ed3733ecde118369601db789d9f7.mp3",
    "bytes": 37152
  },
  {
    "text": "ওজন বাড়ছে না বা কমে যাচ্ছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "7885113514cb94b3cc3a0228eb33f67e",
    "filename": "7885113514cb94b3cc3a0228eb33f67e.mp3",
    "bytes": 11424
  },
  {
    "text": "Refer to ICDS/AWC for growth monitoring. If MUAC < 11.5 cm = RED, refer NRC. Counsel on complementary feeding after 6 months.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "10a1df398f1e5ba69656f53f89c09c88",
    "filename": "10a1df398f1e5ba69656f53f89c09c88.mp3",
    "bytes": 59232
  },
  {
    "text": "রক্তচাপ বেশি বা মাথা ব্যথা হচ্ছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "ff218acc41e8ad8e7b7ed1e94a569c07",
    "filename": "ff218acc41e8ad8e7b7ed1e94a569c07.mp3",
    "bytes": 14304
  },
  {
    "text": "Pre-eclampsia/eclampsia hard-stop. Refer to FRU/DH immediately. Do not give food/water. Lay on left side during transport.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "1a53e6d07984de800ade0328de4ec0c7",
    "filename": "1a53e6d07984de800ade0328de4ec0c7.mp3",
    "bytes": 39072
  },
  {
    "text": "পা বা মুখ ফুলে যাচ্ছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "24d029c7ff7760ddaca35b1a6943761d",
    "filename": "24d029c7ff7760ddaca35b1a6943761d.mp3",
    "bytes": 12096
  },
  {
    "text": "If oedema + headache + BP high = RED (pre-eclampsia). Isolated leg oedema = YELLOW, refer PHC within 24 h for BP check and urine protein.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "3d9abb676b73d3c74b682ec2a3609e9c",
    "filename": "3d9abb676b73d3c74b682ec2a3609e9c.mp3",
    "bytes": 71040
  },
  {
    "text": "রক্তপাত বা তীব্র পেট ব্যথা?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "418867f3bfd7c7d8f33d3d60a3a100b6",
    "filename": "418867f3bfd7c7d8f33d3d60a3a100b6.mp3",
    "bytes": 13824
  },
  {
    "text": "APH hard-stop. Refer to FRU/DH immediately. Any bleeding after 20 weeks = emergency. Do not do vaginal examination.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "29725628450be5b8745398abd315ba87",
    "filename": "29725628450be5b8745398abd315ba87.mp3",
    "bytes": 39360
  },
  {
    "text": "শিশুর নড়াচড়া কমে গেছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "08b200f0714b4b3b8a6c6e5d2f58069a",
    "filename": "08b200f0714b4b3b8a6c6e5d2f58069a.mp3",
    "bytes": 12288
  },
  {
    "text": "Refer to FRU/DH same day for fetal monitoring (CTG/Doppler). Absent fetal movement = emergency.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "1df237fc91decf4b3d0ef3c7c0ffb6c6",
    "filename": "1df237fc91decf4b3d0ef3c7c0ffb6c6.mp3",
    "bytes": 29184
  },
  {
    "text": "তিন মাসের বেশি ANC চেকআপ বাদ গেছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "7c01f303da82c319fd6d3160f63a4f78",
    "filename": "7c01f303da82c319fd6d3160f63a4f78.mp3",
    "bytes": 17280
  },
  {
    "text": "Schedule ANC visit at PHC within 7 days. Check MCP card. Ensure TT, IFA, calcium supplementation are up to date. Flag for PMSMA if HRP.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "8133780d880ba58edcae5650a0cb26a5",
    "filename": "8133780d880ba58edcae5650a0cb26a5.mp3",
    "bytes": 67584
  },
  {
    "text": "চোখে ঝাপসা বা মাথা ঘোরা হচ্ছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "980fcaba826afed3403d9c2bfb76fb86",
    "filename": "980fcaba826afed3403d9c2bfb76fb86.mp3",
    "bytes": 15744
  },
  {
    "text": "Eclampsia prodrome hard-stop. Refer to FRU/DH immediately. Blurred vision + headache + oedema = imminent eclampsia.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "b356ffa8691657bc4bff7952af1cf590",
    "filename": "b356ffa8691657bc4bff7952af1cf590.mp3",
    "bytes": 40416
  },
  {
    "text": "Routine ANC follow-up. Ensure 4 ANC visits (8, 14, 28, 36 weeks). Counsel on IFA (180 tabs), calcium (360 tabs), TT2, diet, birth preparedness. Register on ANMOL.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "923513bf88a4dda4b4504d99256f12fc",
    "filename": "923513bf88a4dda4b4504d99256f12fc.mp3",
    "bytes": 106944
  },
  {
    "text": "অতিরিক্ত রক্তপাত বা দুর্গন্ধযুক্ত স্রাব?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "8cb61739ed43e64d76850092527546d6",
    "filename": "8cb61739ed43e64d76850092527546d6.mp3",
    "bytes": 17472
  },
  {
    "text": "PPH hard-stop. Refer to FRU/DH immediately. If trained: bimanual uterine compression. Misoprostol 600 mcg sublingual if within ASHA scope (confirm at sign-off). Do not delay transport.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "c8c349a608afee1448defc556643fb90",
    "filename": "c8c349a608afee1448defc556643fb90.mp3",
    "bytes": 83808
  },
  {
    "text": "জ্বর বা ঠান্ডা লাগছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "303ff504614a28c736cfa788d7307de6",
    "filename": "303ff504614a28c736cfa788d7307de6.mp3",
    "bytes": 10848
  },
  {
    "text": "Puerperal sepsis risk. Fever + foul discharge = RED. Isolated fever day 1–2 = YELLOW, refer PHC within 24 h. Fever > 38°C after day 2 = RED.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "6128dce292f1174c6fca057c34cbf10e",
    "filename": "6128dce292f1174c6fca057c34cbf10e.mp3",
    "bytes": 99360
  },
  {
    "text": "স্তনে ব্যথা, ফোলা বা লাল দাগ?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "68f546029d94265223f63ccf6156706d",
    "filename": "68f546029d94265223f63ccf6156706d.mp3",
    "bytes": 17952
  },
  {
    "text": "Mastitis: continue breastfeeding, warm compress, refer PHC within 24 h for antibiotics. If abscess (fluctuant swelling) = RED, refer FRU for I&D.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "bc10a51b313e9ae77ad716609c1aae06",
    "filename": "bc10a51b313e9ae77ad716609c1aae06.mp3",
    "bytes": 86880
  },
  {
    "text": "পেটে তীব্র ব্যথা বা সেলাইয়ে সমস্যা?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "bd5a5779336011ba178c9a295097d67b",
    "filename": "bd5a5779336011ba178c9a295097d67b.mp3",
    "bytes": 16032
  },
  {
    "text": "Wound infection = YELLOW, refer PHC within 24 h. Wound dehiscence or severe pain = RED, refer FRU. Peritonitis signs (rigid abdomen, rebound tenderness) = RED hard-stop.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "8785e838e2a4dedecd7e373468e40424",
    "filename": "8785e838e2a4dedecd7e373468e40424.mp3",
    "bytes": 102816
  },
  {
    "text": "প্রস্রাবে জ্বালা বা কষ্ট হচ্ছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "8558dfeda33f9ba2af59db7039c66a05",
    "filename": "8558dfeda33f9ba2af59db7039c66a05.mp3",
    "bytes": 12960
  },
  {
    "text": "UTI: refer PHC within 24 h for urine culture and antibiotics. If fever + flank pain = pyelonephritis → RED, refer FRU.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "63af30c5606afda40b28504639270e09",
    "filename": "63af30c5606afda40b28504639270e09.mp3",
    "bytes": 68928
  },
  {
    "text": "খুব দুর্বল বা মাথা ঘোরা হচ্ছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "5eb0d64d71f89a3789ac960a7691bd74",
    "filename": "5eb0d64d71f89a3789ac960a7691bd74.mp3",
    "bytes": 12768
  },
  {
    "text": "Assess pallor (conjunctiva, palms). Severe pallor = anaemia → YELLOW, refer PHC for Hb check. Hb < 7 g/dL or fainting = RED, refer FRU for transfusion.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "25d80ae88ca71171c16d3955f0aef4fc",
    "filename": "25d80ae88ca71171c16d3955f0aef4fc.mp3",
    "bytes": 163968
  },
  {
    "text": "শিশুর বয়স কত মাস?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "bb52c7896b36d823b7b1e4fb802e42f4",
    "filename": "bb52c7896b36d823b7b1e4fb802e42f4.mp3",
    "bytes": 10368
  },
  {
    "text": "Schedule catch-up at nearest session site within 7 days. BCG can be given up to 1 year. OPV/IPV/Pentavalent: give missed dose, continue schedule. Do not restart series.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "8fc53d7925b8f441ec432d4b14714967",
    "filename": "8fc53d7925b8f441ec432d4b14714967.mp3",
    "bytes": 51168
  },
  {
    "text": "কোন টিকা মিস হয়েছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "554c3d58be7028d100047a8fe417d2af",
    "filename": "554c3d58be7028d100047a8fe417d2af.mp3",
    "bytes": 10848
  },
  {
    "text": "Schedule catch-up within 7 days. Measles-1 at 9 months, Vitamin A 1 lakh IU at 9 months. If > 12 months, give MMR instead of measles.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "4146b377544fc684586591c55a8707d1",
    "filename": "4146b377544fc684586591c55a8707d1.mp3",
    "bytes": 79296
  },
  {
    "text": "কতদিন আগে টিকা দেওয়ার কথা ছিল?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "2f68020e0d33102f7c79f5e9e2a3393b",
    "filename": "2f68020e0d33102f7c79f5e9e2a3393b.mp3",
    "bytes": 12960
  },
  {
    "text": "Catch-up immunisation. Do not restart series. Give missed dose and continue from where left off. Refer to PHC for catch-up session. Flag on ANMOL for tracking.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "d4848790a7e744e18e52ee34bae0fbe7",
    "filename": "d4848790a7e744e18e52ee34bae0fbe7.mp3",
    "bytes": 51840
  },
  {
    "text": "শিশুর কি কোনো অসুস্থতা আছে এখন?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "c289d9721e68ec3be004aa9e575268a9",
    "filename": "c289d9721e68ec3be004aa9e575268a9.mp3",
    "bytes": 12960
  },
  {
    "text": "Mild illness (mild fever, cold) = vaccinate as scheduled. Moderate/severe illness = defer vaccination until recovered. Reschedule within 7 days of recovery. Do not miss opportunity for mild illness.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "9a03a8ce2595a350441136f6162a40a6",
    "filename": "9a03a8ce2595a350441136f6162a40a6.mp3",
    "bytes": 75360
  },
  {
    "text": "১-৫ বছর বয়সী শিশুর বুস্টার ডোজ মিস হয়েছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "e97b0db7627a41eb84f269181f334722",
    "filename": "e97b0db7627a41eb84f269181f334722.mp3",
    "bytes": 20064
  },
  {
    "text": "DPT booster at 16–24 months. OPV booster at 16–24 months. MMR at 15–18 months. Vitamin A 6-monthly up to 5 years. Schedule catch-up at next session.",
